呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e833d131e70ed15f347446fff4fe452af8222bb3","tid":587093,"uid":163558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:35:53.000Z","msg":"永遠平心靜氣想佢同傾佢都話我怪緊佢<br />\n我好辛苦啊大佬 徘徊喺想散同唔散中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf4bf9ec8d47452014fb335ff773aec6c21fa39","tid":587093,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:14:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9797159deba3ce0883f023879cb2b182f6032019","tid":587093,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"84587f34f74b3f6828f7fdc48ff2dad16dfc5067","tid":587093,"uid":82576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:39:19.000Z","msg":"借ac一問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對大家有意嘅女仔呢排學業上好忙好煩 自問都做足有哄佢有安慰佢 佢hea應都冇怪佢 但係佢始終唔肯講煩乜同平時一樣自己死頂 今日朝早就同我講話唔好等佢 話自己太忙太攰所以叫我走 挽留佢佢都淨係話都想見大家但係要等佢平復返 應該要點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:大家都係對方初戀"},{"pid":"0cb88cbcd5ffd7610da3a505d8032d203f835f1c","tid":587093,"uid":149357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T11:16:53.000Z","msg":"點樣係夾點樣係唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a537ea12aec1327d37fe702c3ee853b5d659e0","tid":587093,"uid":127145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T11:20:29.000Z","msg":"男朋友就係話我同佢唔夾<br />\n<br />\n經歷幾多野都分開<br />\n<br />\n以為佢係將來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609f08044b9521594884cadd9b818f9d39615f51","tid":587093,"uid":120937,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:04:28.000Z","msg":"都係同另一半唔夾，價值觀有差異，好多時候溝通唔到，相處開始攰，係咪應該分手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756c96325a1869af8790c551e1ed15e87b007e42","